com.thesonofthom.maps

Class WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEHeaderMap.PEOptionalHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.thesonofthom.tools.Buffer
      • com.thesonofthom.tools.BufferMap
        • com.thesonofthom.maps.WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEHeaderMap.PEOptionalHeader
  • Enclosing class:
    WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEHeaderMap

    public class WinExeFileHeaderMap.PEHeaderMap.PEOptionalHeader
extends BufferMap
    Map to parse the "PE Optional Header" in the header.

    The "PE Optional Header" is not "optional" per se, because it is required in Executable files, but not in COFF object files

    Same as the IMAGE_OPTIONAL_HEADER32 and IMAGE_OPTIONAL_HEADER64 structs in WinNT.h
